    "The proposed method ensures that the model does not use the protected attribute to make predictions, thereby reducing bias in the data [112].",
    "Balancing instance distributionLastly, With the goal of accurate image classification models, Yang et al.",
    "introduce a two-step approach to filtering and balancing the distribution of images in the popular Imagenet dataset of people from different subgroups [91].",
    "In the filtering step, they remove inappropriate images that reinforce harmful stereotypes or depict people in degrading ways.",
    "In the balancing step, they adjust the distribution of images from different racial and gender subgroups to ensure that the dataset represents each subgroup equally."
